<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog - Skill Sharing Platform</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url(man.jpg);
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .container { 
            max-width: 1700px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            padding: 20px; 
            background-color: rgba(189, 183, 183, 0.5);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .logout {
            background-color: #007bff;
        }
        .nav {
            background-color: rgb(176, 180, 173);
        }
        .home {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }

        .nav-container {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .nav-container a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-container a:hover {
            background-color: #1976D2;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .logout-link {
            display: block;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #1976D2;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #1976D2;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #155a8a;
        }

        /* Blog Section */
        .blog-post {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(184, 181, 208, 0.5);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .blog-post h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .blog-post p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .blog-post .tags {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .tags span {
            background-color: #1976D2;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        /* Comments Section */
        .comments-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .comments-section h4 {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .comment {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #9d9c9c;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .comment p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .comment-author {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .comment-input {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .comment-input textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .comment-input button {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #1976D2;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .comment-input button:hover {
            background-color: #155a8a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/main" class="home">Home</a>
            <a href="/user-portal" class="nav">User Portal</a>
            <a href="/tutor-dashboard" class="nav">Tutor Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/admin-panel" class="nav">Admin Panel</a>
            <a href="/landing-page" class="nav">Landing Page</a>
            <a href="/blog" class="nav">Blog</a>
            <a href="/logout" class="logout">Logout</a>
        </div>

        <h1>Blog</h1>

        <h2>Articles and Tutorials</h2>
        <div class="blog-post">
            <h3>Getting Started with Python Programming</h3>
            <p>Python is a powerful programming language used in a variety of applications...</p>
            <div class="tags">
                <span>#Python</span> <span>#Programming</span> <span>#Tutorial</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Industry News and Updates</h2>
        <div class="blog-post">
            <h3>Latest in Technology: AI Advancements in 2024</h3>
            <p>Artificial Intelligence is reshaping industries across the globe...</p>
            <div class="tags">
                <span>#AI</span> <span>#TechNews</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Success Stories and Testimonials</h2>
        <div class="blog-post">
            <h3>How John Became a Successful Python Developer</h3>
            <p>John started with no knowledge of programming and now works for a top tech firm...</p>
            <div class="tags">
                <span>#SuccessStory</span> <span>#Testimonial</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Comments Section -->
        <div class="comments-section">
            <h4>Comments</h4>
            <div class="comment">
                <p class="comment-author">Alice</p>
                <p>This blog post is really helpful. Thanks for sharing!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="comment">
                <p class="comment-author">Bob</p>
                <p>Looking forward to more tutorials on Python.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Comment Input -->
            <div class="comment-input">
                <h4>Leave a Comment</h4>
                <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Type your comment here..."></textarea>
                <button>Submit Comment</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/logout" class="logout-link">Logout</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
